  "original_title": "Inflation soars to 64.3% in August",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inflation soars to 64.3% in August",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Department of Census and Statistics says that the overall rate of inflation as measured by CCPI on y-o-y basis in August is 64.3%.",
        "According to the Department, the overall rate of inflation is 64.3% in August 2022 and the CCPI inflation, on an y-o-y basis which was calculated for the month of July 2022 was 60.8%.",
        "The Year on Year inflation of Food Group increased to 93.7% in August 2022 from 90.9% in July 2022 and the Year on Year inflation of Non Food Group increased to 50.2% in August 2022 from 46.5% in July 2022.",
        "The month on month change was contributed by increases of Food items by 0.83% and Non-Food items by 1.62% respectively.",
        "One-month-old infant abandoned at a motor garage with a letter",
        "Are you a victim of Cyber Crime? Police Unit ready to crackdown crime in the cyberspace"
      ],
